{"word":"H1369 - גְּבוּרָה - gᵉbûwrâh - gheb-oo-raw' - Force","slug":"H1369","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גְּבוּרָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gᵉbûwrâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gheb-oo-raw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Force"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05D4; - <a href='S:g'>g</a><sup>e</sup>bu&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h</b> - <i>gheb-oo-raw'</i><p/>Feminine passive participle from the same as <a href=\"#/H1368\">H1368</a>; <i>force</i> (literally or figuratively); by implication <i>valor</i>, <i>victory: - </i>force, mastery, might, mighty (act, power), power, strength."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1368\">H1368</a>, <a href=\"#/H1376\">H1376</a>, <a href=\"#/H1377\">H1377</a>, <a href=\"#/H1396\">H1396</a>, <a href=\"#/H1397\">H1397</a>, <a href=\"#/H1398\">H1398</a>, <a href=\"#/H1399\">H1399</a>, <a href=\"#/H1402\">H1402</a>, <a href=\"#/H1403\">H1403</a>, <a href=\"#/H1404\">H1404</a>"}]}